('10052967', 'applestore', '', 'Also a Victim of Automatic Password Reset. And having set up my account eight years ago with an email address which is now defunct, my DropBox (\"Pro\" — for which I paid $99/year) account is now effectively rendered kaput. Their customer service is absolutely nonexistent; after being caught up in a spaghetti of FAQ and self-help pages I finally figured out how to fill out a \"support ticket\" and — received no response to it at all. There is no way to contact an actual human being at this company on the phone, not even a \"chat\" option. I used their paid service several times a day for years and, well, now having been effectively \"serviced\" by them, will not use it any longer.', 'gp:AOqpTOFPsfKA7PxLM5hG28aAjjzGJvg8vtgBM6pi_9aaENTglTpDgRsbIDqrCPBPxIErIwffyRwXODrZCG3b1W', 'googleplay', '', 'Time On', 'Dropbox', 0.0283791, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-16 17:12:37', 3, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
