('108316423', 'applestore', '', 'Switching to Google Drive I used to love how fast and easy my photos would upload from my IPhone. I then noticed several months ago each picture would take 30 seconds or longer and the pictures remaining would increase. It was really frustrating because it used to work so well.  I came here to see if other people were having the same issue and I was very surprised to see how many bad reviews there are and people discussing Google Drive. I decided to give it a try and I am uploading around 5 seconds per picture. I\'ve been using Drop Box for over 5 years and was happy with it until now. Good bye Drop Box!', 'gp:AOqpTOFCUmgelUNPk8OqiPZY79q7_0wYrbIKmMXoYbb37WO3tN29N9gPqV8bJvHWjaJ0y0_P6102-nhKgWaveU', 'googleplay', '', 'Awesome I like it very much.I\'ve been using dropbox from 3 years', 'Dropbox', 0.156915, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-18 17:10:37', 98, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
