('108467156', 'applestore', 'Request', 'I really like the app for the watch, I just wish y\'all could add the channels to it too. I know it\'s on a smaller screen and not as much computing power as the phone app, but sending slacks in the channels and not just replying to DMs and mentions would be a great addition', 'gp:AOqpTOGsQwRtTqkiM2UN-l2rdC7cj8Rjfce1HTJXUQjPevmK-rNXDne0oZhv7JPIagpOUG-rzlowweFZ1sgl3K', 'googleplay', 'Good app', 'One really frustrating bug though: i\'ll often get notifications of direct messages that don\'t exist, from people I have never direct messaged. The red 9+ bubble stays constantly on my mentions making it hard to tell if i actually have anythin new! These notifications disappear if I look at them on the web page, but appear again on the app. Have tried logging out, reinstalling, no luck.', 'Slack', 0.133256, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-18 17:11:28', 100, 2, -1, 0.625, 'ot', 'br'),
('10876341', 'applestore', 'No update description?', 'App is fine but for such a critical piece of software to my business, I need to make decisions on updating or not based off of current changes. Sending people to a website that they must manually enter into a browser in order to see the change log is lazy, unprofessional, and an inefficient use of your customers\' time.\n\nIf this doesn\'t change soon I will be forced to consider competitive options.', '10155101678661756_10155156783846756', 'facebook', '', 'And this was your customer service reply to my inquiry? Sounds like it\'s time to go to the media...\n\nHi there,\n\nYes, this reply is automated. And yes, we understand that might be frustrating to hear.\n\nTruth is we\'d love to chat one-on-one. But we\'ve got a totally revamped self-serve tool, and it really is the best path to the fastest, most relevant answer to your question.\n\nSimply click this link and select the issue that best describes your question. You\'ll see steps to take to resolve your issue or what information we need from you to help. You\'ll be Dropboxing again in no time.', 'Dropbox', 0.200332, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-18 17:12:34', 101, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
