('161054877', 'applestore', 'Best nav by a longshot', 'It\'s pretty great, I like how well it routes me around bad traffic and I would normally give it 5 Stars...The only problem i have with it is that in the latest versions, there is no longer an option to use GPS only when using the app. So this means the app keeps sucking power all day long when you aren\'t using it. I don\'t utilize any of the features that would require the app to always use the GPS and I really wish we could still set the location setting to \'while using\'\n\nGive me back that feature and I\'ll bump my review back up to 5 stars\n\nUpdate: still hogging the battery when not in use. I would really appreciate the option to not have this app run in the background. For now, just turn off location services when I\'m not using the app.', 'gp:AOqpTOGwjN870KeTvINaH-o5duBfY6FvMvmk8UQNSLf5X1h_j8wxqgiS5PQVfm6c0pZsAXMRVK7wTItC7XAFUw', 'googleplay', '', 'Great app but the most recent update broke a few things. It\'s now a huge battery suck - to the point where my car charger can\'t keep up. It\'s also significantly slower to load and if I close it before reaching my destination (like I now have to so I can preserve battery life) it doesn\'t remember my destination so I have to enter it again. It used to pop up a message asking if I was still heading to X and that\'s gone.', 'Waze', 0.219505, 2, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 08:45:23', 186, 2, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('163122245', 'applestore', 'Now routing through town', 'I\'ve used Waze for almost 3 years now. With the resent updates it now routes me through town on my way home, taking me off the highway. This is my daily route so I know it\'s 5 minutes slower. It\'s doing it for my husband as well. I contacted Waze, and they were so not helpful even though I jumped through all their hoops, and did all their steps. They suggested I do alternate routes, which reroute me even farther away, never going on the highway. Makes me think they are getting paired to take different routes to drive by businesses. Hope they fix this, but it makes me question all the routes they give me when I\'m not sure which is the best way to go.', '87375117', 'applestore', 'Best navigation app and free!', 'By far this app is the best navigation app for multiple languages and in or outside the country.  The only thing I HATE about this app is that it requires the GPS to be on all the time even when your not using the app.  Having the GPS on all the time make my phone over heat and  it drains my battery.  Bad decision on wazes part.  Now I  have turn the GPS on when I use it and off when done. REALLY ANNOYING!!!', 'Waze', 0.220842, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 08:46:55', 187, 0, -2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
