('227973660732160_558389884357201', 'facebook', '', 'I have Spotify Premium. Bought the subscription on my credit card. I liked it so much that I also bought a subscription for my wife on my credit card. So I get billed for two subscriptions on my card and we both have accounts. About three months ago my wife was suddenly unable to access her account. She hasn\'t been able to access it since. I\'m still being billed for two accounts, but only mine seems to be working. Can anyone help?', '796028423650963456', 'twitter', '', '@spotifycares I moved to Canada and I cant change my credit card for the premium account. Says that it hasnt been released in Canada.', 'Spotify', 0.22171, 1, 1, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:35:40', 241, 2, 0, 0.75, 'br', 'ot'),
