('227973660732160_561417194054470', 'facebook', '', 'I need some help.  I\'m trying to access my account, either on my computer or my phone. It says my email is already signed up, but I cant access anything regarding my account. When I try to reset my password, it says it \"looks like I\'m trying to access my account through my Facebook account\", which I\'m not.  At this point, I\'d be happy cancelling all my known accounts, so I could just start over.  Please help.', '561406340722222_561428077386715', 'facebook', '', 'That\'s the thing. I don\'t know my username, which takes me to my yahoo.com email, which won\'t work. Do I just need to start the spotify account over with a new email account?', 'Spotify', 0.320054, 1, 1, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:36:51', 243, 0, 0, 1, 'br', 'ot'),
('227973660732160_562663387263184', 'facebook', '', 'I\'m trying to set up premium for family. Entering my credit card info and nothing happens.', '227973660732160_560218884174301', 'facebook', '', 'Spotify is a great app and I want to upgrade my account to premium but my credit card is from vietnam which is not on spotify countries list, can I use that credit to pay and if I can\'t what should I do to get the premium, please help me', 'Spotify', 0.291049, 1, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:37:18', 244, 0, 2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
('227973660732160_568992363296953', 'facebook', '', 'I want to cancel my Spotify subscription before I get charged but I cannot login to Spotify - it does not recognize any of my email accounts.  I signed up for a free 30 day trial period, directly at Spotify website.  this required my credit card # to charge after the trial period.  My 30 days is almost up but I can\'t cancel because they don\'t recognize my addresses.', '570239506505572_570287553167434', 'facebook', '', 'That sucks. Apple does I don\'t get how you can get away with not matching them. So if I sign up for a single account trial I can\'t change it to family without getting charged till the 90 days is up???', 'Spotify', 0.227066, 1, 2, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:38:31', 245, -1, -1, 1, 'ot', 'br'),
