('233536693', 'applestore', 'Bugs and Problems', 'I love Spotify, but after more than a year of being premium I have noticed many things that bother me... First of all Spotify consumes a lot of data even if the songs are downloaded, it looks like this is caused by album covers being downloaded every time... Second there should be an option to delete some downloaded songs from your playlist without actually deleting them from your playlist so you can free up some space... At last but not least, the shuffle option is the worst I\'ve ever seen in a music app, a song can be easily repeated after two songs and It looks like every time I press shuffle it plays just a few of my songs and forgets about all the others.\n\nPlease Spotify, fix all these problems!!!', '573702652825924_573759912820198', 'facebook', '', 'I\'m seriously questioning what the purpose is of following artist when Spotify can\'t really provide a true overview of new releases. And even worse, you inject \"suggestions\" based on my listening pattern.', 'Spotify', 0.0871344, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:42:20', 252, 0, -1, 0.875, 'br', 'ot'),
('236924082', 'applestore', 'Becoming unreliable', 'The app is becoming more and more unreliable. It randomly drops the Bluetooth even when the Bluetooth is working for phone calls.  It used to be when that happened it would default to the speaker but now it is sometimes defaulting to the phone and more often making no sound at all. It\'s unpredictability is making me concerned whether it\'s safe to use app since I need to look at screen to determine whether it is working.', '804041911489167360', 'twitter', '', '@waze @FFDP all the way!!!!', 'Waze', 0.0503002, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:43:09', 253, 0, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('239679926', 'applestore', 'App Storage Space Issue', 'When I transfer documents from my phone to Dropbox to free up space, the size of my Dropbox app grows accordingly.  Totally counterproductive and needs to be fixed', '10155037319751756_10155097954591756', 'facebook', '', 'Two years ago Dropbox gave free space, that is ok, but now it is being withdrawn, so I have to either pay 99USD or to delete or loose all saved files. I think it is unfair and looks like smart fox behavior, so I don\'t trust anymore for such \"free\" services.. I feel very disappointed (', 'Dropbox', 0.120828, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 13:44:01', 254, 0, -1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
