('39406568', 'applestore', 'Always uses your location (and battery)', 'I lol he app but the newer version uses more battery because of location services are always on for Waze. Even when I power down WAZE the arrow still appears on the top right of my iPhone indicating an app is using my location. Once I go to privacy and select NEVER under location services for Waze does it turn off. It would be very convenient if Waze added a \"While using App\" option.', '797640609079005184', 'twitter', '', '@waze okay is there any way to make it so Waze uses location services only while using the app because you are *killing* my battery', 'Waze', 0.441248, 3, 1, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 14:57:03', 340, 1, -1, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
