('490747876', 'applestore', 'Good, but not good enough', 'Before the update, there was one ad every half hour, and that was fine, but now, there\'s an ad every 2 songs or so. Your best bet is to use your free Spotify premium trial and then use it for as much as possible in the next 7 days and just forget about it. Then the trial ends, and you\'re stuck with the same annoying ads, limited skips, and you have to keep your music in shuffle. On top of that, you can\'t even keep your music downloaded and that\'s just a deal breaker.', '536272842', 'applestore', 'Best. App. Ever.', 'Omg this is an amazing app and I love the fact that you can listen to your favorite artist and just their own music', 'Spotify', 0.242099, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 15:54:37', 427, 0, 2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
