('5239892', 'applestore', 'Love it', 'I have the family plan and LOVE IT!! Also love the app!\nSupport is great, very responsive! Every time I\'ve made a suggestion on improvements it always happens within the next few updates. I realize one day I will ask for something impossible but until then...\n\nWishList for Updates; \nI have a lot of playlists, it would be nice to be able to add one song to multiple playlists at one time.\nI like being able to see the top five most popular songs for each artist but wish there was a way to go to a list of all the artists song and see the songs in order of popularity.', 'gp:AOqpTOHRTl7GQDG3F8jp9CTj3xXLtjKkZdv4XIut6SARE1ncJzxxp8IQzaWETMR80ol2_LGRmDWq87GmnAcsuw', 'googleplay', 'It\'s great but there are some bugs', 'I have Spotify premium and in my downloaded music it will randomly not let me listen to songs that I may have downloaded months before. I\'ll have to flip the download toggle and then I end up having to re-download like half of my library. Plus sometimes it forces me to use cellular to download. If these issues were fixed then this would go back to being an easy 5-star rating.', 'Spotify', 0.203399, 0, 0, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 17:29:00', 450, 3, 2, 0.875, 'ot', 'br'),
