('537176681', 'applestore', 'FRUSTRATED!!', 'I loved this app for several months, but then it started playing completely random songs in the middle of playlists I\'d created!  I\'d try to listen to Christmas music and it would start playing a random song from 1970 that I\'d never heard of!  Not only does it play completely random songs, it doesn\'t play just one or two, it plays like 8 in a row!! Seriously?! I wish it would at least base the \"random\" songs after the playlist I\'m listening to! ?Now that I\'ve ranted, I would like to say that Spotify is a good app that allows you to listen to your favorite music and *mostly* just your favorite.  It allows you to choose from many songs to create playlists and other such things.  I\'d definitely recommend it to anyone who doesn\'t want to pay to listen to music.', '350386389', 'applestore', 'It\'s aight', 'Pros: all the music I want at my fingertips. I love the discover feature. Daily playlists are rad. I\'ve found a lot of new and great music through them both. \n\nCons: not a fan of the ui. I\'d like it to be easier to jump to an artist by tapping on their name or icon rather than pulling up a menu. Old phone means app is often unresponsive when not connected to wifi. Support is cumbersome- like, please just let me contact a human because I\'m paying money for your service and I don\'t want to spend an hour combing thru the message board for solutions. That said, once you do come in contact with a human they will solve your issue fast and in a friendly manner, so add that to the pros list', 'Spotify', 0.202121, 1, 1, 1, 2, '2017-02-21 17:40:26', 484, 1, 1, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
